:name: Expresso
:description: Expresso firmware interactive simulation script.
:           : Load this script in the Renode monitor with:
:           :   i @tests/renode/scripts/expresso.resc
:           : or override the ELF path:
:           :   $bin=@/path/to/expresso-fw.elf i @tests/renode/scripts/expresso.resc

using sysbus

# Default ELF path – points to the release build from the workspace root.
# Override by setting $bin before sourcing this script.
$bin ?= @target/thumbv7em-none-eabihf/release/expresso-fw.elf

$name ?= "expresso"
mach create $name

machine LoadPlatformDescription @tests/renode/platforms/stm32g431cb.repl

# Open a terminal window for USART1 (DIN MIDI physical layer).
# In a headless / CI run this can be omitted; the Robot test uses
# CreateTerminalTester instead.
showAnalyzer sysbus.usart1

macro reset
"""
    sysbus LoadELF $bin
"""

runMacro $reset
